
Revision history for Perl module Mojo::IOLoop::HoboProcess.

0.005 Fri Apr 28 18:00:00 EST 2017

  * Disabled timeout testing on the Windows platform.

0.004 Fri Mar 17 06:30:00 EST 2017

  * Bumped MCE::Shared dependency to 1.817 for improved reliability
    with Mojolicious 7.25 and later releases.

0.003 Thu Feb 16 04:00:00 EST 2017

  * Improved reliability with recent Mojolicious releases
    (same bug fixed by jberger in Mojo::IOLoop::Subprocess).

  * Added inherited test from Mojolicious-7.26/t/mojo/subprocess.t.

  * Bumped MCE::Shared dependency to 1.808.
  * Bumped Mojolicious dependency to 7.07.

0.002 Wed Nov 23 16:00:00 EST 2016

  * Bumped MCE::Shared dependency to 1.807.
  * Improved reliability.

0.001 Thu Nov 03 04:00:00 EST 2016

  * First release.

